      "sections": [
        {
          "id": 30536,
          "title": "Overview",
          "body_text": "Arcanotron Custos controls players with its [Ethereal Shackles] and by creating pools of [Arcane Residue]. Upon running out of energy, Arcanotron Custos begins its [Refueling Protocol], drawing in [Energy Orbs] to refuel itself.",
          "sections": [
            {
              "id": 30537,
              "title": "Damage Dealers",
              "body_text": "$bullet;[Arcane Expulsion] inflicts a heavy amount of damage and knocks back all players.\r\n$bullet;[Arcane Residue] inflicts heavy damage to players standing in the area.\r\n$bullet; Arcanotron Custos gains [Arcane Empowerment] if an Energy Orb reaches it."
            },
            {
              "id": 30538,
              "title": "Healers",
              "body_text": "$bullet;[Ethereal Shackles] roots players and inflicts periodic damage.\r\n$bullet;[Arcane Residue] inflicts heavy damage to players standing in the area.\r\n$bullet; Arcanotron Custos gains [Arcane Empowerment] if an Energy Orb reaches it."
            },
            {
              "id": 30539,
              "title": "Tanks",
              "body_text": "$bullet;[Repulsing Slam] inflicts a heavy amount of damage and knocks back its target.\r\n$bullet;[Arcane Residue] inflicts heavy damage to players standing in the area.\r\n$bullet; Arcanotron Custos gains [Arcane Empowerment] if an Energy Orb reaches it."
            }
          ]
