      "sections": [
        {
          "id": 30540,
          "title": "Overview",
          "body_text": "At the start of the encounter and 50% remaining health, Gemellus uses [Triplicate] to create clones that drift around the arena. Gemellus and its clones are bound by a [Synaptic Nexus] and act as one.",
          "sections": [
            {
              "id": 35354,
              "title": "Damage Dealers",
              "body_text": "\r\n$bullet;[Astral Grasp] pulls players towards their respective Gemellus.\r\n$bullet;[Cosmic Sting] inflicts heavy damage and creates [Void Secretions]."
            },
            {
              "id": 35243,
              "title": "Damage Dealers",
              "body_text": "\r\n$bullet;[Astral Grasp] pulls players towards their respective Gemellus.\r\n$bullet;[Cosmic Sting] inflicts heavy damage and creates [Void Secretions]."
            },
            {
              "id": 30541,
              "title": "Damage Dealers",
              "body_text": "\r\n$bullet;[Astral Grasp] pulls players towards their respective Gemellus.\r\n$bullet;[Cosmic Sting] inflicts moderate damage and creates [Void Secretions] upon expiration."
            },
            {
              "id": 35355,
              "title": "Healers",
              "body_text": "\r\n$bullet;[Cosmic Sting] inflicts heavy damage and creates [Void Secretions].\r\n$bullet;[Astral Grasp] pulls players towards their respective Gemellus."
            },
            {
