      "sections": [
        {
          "id": 30548,
          "title": "Overview",
          "body_text": "Degentrius leads the assault from atop Magisters' Terrace, commanding the platform with overwhelming Void magic. [Void Torrent] streams carve across the arena as they flow into Degentrius, while [Unstable Void Essence]s ricochet around the platform.",
          "sections": [
            {
              "id": 30549,
              "title": "Damage Dealers",
              "body_text": "$bullet; If there are no players standing under [Unstable Void Essence]  when it impacts, damage will be inflicted to all players.\r\n$bullet; [Void Torrent]  inflicts moderate damage and stuns any players that come into contact with it."
            },
            {
              "id": 30550,
              "title": "Healers",
              "body_text": "$bullet; [Devouring Entropy] creates Entropy Orbs upon removal.\r\n$bullet; If there are no players standing under [Unstable Void Essence]  when it impacts, damage will be inflicted to all players.\r\n$bullet; [Void Torrent]  inflicts moderate damage and stuns any players that come into contact with it."
            },
            {
              "id": 30551,
              "title": "Tanks",
              "body_text": "$bullet; [Null Bomb] will inflict massive damage to all players if it is not triggered by a player.\r\n$bullet; If there are no players standing under [Unstable Void Essence]  when it impacts, damage will be inflicted to all players.\r\n$bullet; [Void Torrent]  inflicts moderate damage and stuns any players that come into contact with it."
            }
          ]
        },
